{"tid":2164163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛知縣女性於自宅發現骸骨 懷疑是失蹤5年的同居兄長","createTime":"2020-08-19T05:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T08:30:18.000Z","uid":48631,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"84e290836b45e27df7cc430870a9b6ca6b8f0f81","tid":2164163,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"8月15日愛知縣春日井市某住宅發生骸骨發現案，懷疑屍體屬於住在該宅的一名男子。該名男子在四年前已被列為失蹤人口。<br />\n<br />\n愛知縣警8月15日下午五時接春日井市一名69歲女性報警求肋，指自己在房間內發現疑似人骨。警察到場後在凌亂的房間中找到已經白骨化、沒有穿著衣服的遺體。<br />\n<br />\n據女性所述，她和一兄一弟三人一同居住，兄長在五年前失蹤，並在四年前列作失蹤人口。女性當時正在打掃兄長的房間，其後在房間內發現已經白骨化的遺體。警方相信這具遺體很大機會是女性失蹤多年的兄長，確認死者身分和調查工作仍在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/life/4me-by-gu-cosmetic/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Flife%2F4me-by-gu-cosmetic%2F&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInP7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=775be059\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/life/4me-by-gu-cosmetic/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細佬殺左阿哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92af3bdfe36ebe9daf9e80813eed8f5e94bf910","tid":2164163,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:25:28.000Z","msg":"沒有穿著衣服的遺體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf692a2f49a588da49e4db4cb4486ecbce527a9","tid":2164163,"uid":39383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"失蹤咁耐係房度搵返, 又話一齊住?"},{"pid":"03963f91e81b1c25c78cdfee798e1d833941f019","tid":2164163,"uid":317202,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:26:08.000Z","msg":"屋企要幾大先可以有條屍都發現唔到<br />\n事隔5年，第一次打掃入房顯然是不可能<br />\n期間一定有入過房但係發現唔到"},{"pid":"ea28c9faa9495bc6d07cdf95b5fd6e3482c9abd9","tid":2164163,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"你條link錯左"},{"pid":"55a7a706dd2e36fdc2a40ae363a9e3d8309f761c","tid":2164163,"uid":8014,"like":